{"tid":2500639,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交友App陷阱｜直撃MK中醫妹 　陪睇醫生sell投資劏客","createTime":"2021-04-22T22:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T23:46:04.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6cbc6aac5246bb020ace72feb07c424e4e23e4","tid":2500639,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T22:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2B2197a-tDbfSKa_DreS135wwWU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WTETPISSQNCC5PSSVBMMLIOEPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2B2197a-tDbfSKa_DreS135wwWU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWTETPISSQNCC5PSSVBMMLIOEPQ.jpg&h=5f47bcf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當得知記者有意看中醫，Heidi即興奮約見面，同日帶記者上門看中醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RbkvY6TRCu0mXZw_XJSUxAbbeVQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IZQOO46WEJHAFIZFKSOFIGHPOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRbkvY6TRCu0mXZw_XJSUxAbbeVQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIZQOO46WEJHAFIZFKSOFIGHPOY.jpg&h=a391575a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHeidi除劏客見中醫，亦會帶客到HKUE學校推銷收費逾萬元的課程。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n疫情影響美容院被數度勒令停業，疑有推銷集團伺機擴展掠水業務，殺入中醫界。「中醫妹」經交友App釣客後，噓寒問暖故作曖昧，目的為氹客看中醫，即使無病無痛，仍被游說預繳逾萬元、長達一年的中醫藥費，「美容院呃人就聽過，估唔到中醫都呃人。」中醫妹更會連環劏客，數日內再推銷過萬元的教育課程。《蘋果》放蛇約見「中醫妹」直擊氹客過程，她吹噓該為明星中醫，醫術幾乎萬能，「有朋友濕疹嚴重到流晒膿、血水，差唔多要切腳趾，最後睇醫師，而家結焦。」之後亦游說記者報讀學費近2萬元的投資課程。<br />\n<br />\nJacky去年12月經交友App結識女網友，交談數天即被帶到旺角周大福商業中心推銷投資課程，由於他無興趣報讀，該女網友即場介紹另一職員Heidi給他。Heidi開始日夜關懷他的身體狀況，不久後帶他到旺角看中醫。<br />\n「醫師就開啲調理身體中藥畀我，叫我兩星期覆診一次。」Jacky憶述診症後，職員即落力游說「調理身體機能」療程。「佢話免診金，半年要萬零蚊。」即使表明仍是學生無力支付，職員仍稱可分期付款，最終誘他簽卡，惟他無力還卡數，現由母親協助還款。<br />\n「冇病冇痛要睇半年，仲要成萬蚊。」Jacky服食一個多月中藥粉後，開始質疑受騙，認為Heidi為賺佣金才帶他看中醫，「我可能畀佢昆咗。」他不憤：「美容院呃人就聽過，估唔到中醫都呃人。」<br />\n以交友App撈客推銷以往常見於美容或健身療程，惟近半年交友App湧現一堆「中醫妹」、「中醫仔」搵食，令一心交友的純情男女被氹落沓，預繳高額中醫療程。記者經事主聯絡「中醫妹」Heidi，「地鐵站好大廣告嘅醫學美容中心，背後有佢哋support，係友好集團。」她甫見面即鼓起如簧之舌，「友好集團幫手搵甄醫師，佢70歲，行醫好多年，睇開明星嘅醫生，幫過周潤發、米雪，佢本身退休，老細搵佢返嚟幫手。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrRvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=7418794a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2F7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM%2F&h=edece58b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/7GBYBH4OHFHJXNBCKO4HXB4NOM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/QDSXW56OFFEFRDKJOOCIKWBCKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2FQDSXW56OFFEFRDKJOOCIKWBCKE%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrRvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=2106efec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210423%2FQDSXW56OFFEFRDKJOOCIKWBCKE%2F&h=c7adfd79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210423/QDSXW56OFFEFRDKJOOCIKWBCKE/</a>"},{"pid":"909a2a2a41d69360fedb8e019a6da06e56690bdd","tid":2500639,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T22:36:31.000Z","msg":"又係交友apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又呃d9痕西痕"},{"pid":"c0086dffa62aceb9226963679ecb268bde36f5a7","tid":2500639,"uid":20279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T22:43:26.000Z","msg":"人類總是要犯同樣的錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f249ba54659eccab0f2f051c3f88c9779c749e","tid